<section id="about" class="w-full bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-6 py-24 md:py-28 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] md:gap-16">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-5 text-muted">Who we are</p>
        <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal leading-[1.2] text-ink md:text-4xl">
          A small firm that stays close to the work
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-lg leading-[1.85] text-ink/90">
          Listening is where our work begins. We take the time to understand
          your concerns so we can focus on the things that matter most to you.
          Our job is to help you make sound financial, investment, and business
          decisions, and to leave you better equipped to make the next ones
          yourself.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-[1.85] text-ink/90">
          Our purpose is to protect and grow your business and your long-term
          financial security. Because we are a small firm, the person who
          studies your problem is the same person who works through it with you.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 border-t border-line/60 pt-10 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow mb-3 text-muted">Our vision</p>
            <p class="font-heading text-xl leading-[1.45] text-ink">
              To be the most trusted advisory firm in the region.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow mb-3 text-muted">Our mission</p>
            <p class="font-heading text-xl leading-[1.45] text-ink">
              To strengthen the financial security and growth of individuals and
              businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
